docs {
  # Update Password
  
  Updates the user's password. Requires current password for security.
  All refresh tokens will be revoked after password change.
  
  **Authentication:** Required (JWT cookie)
  
  **Request Body:**
  ```json
  {
    "currentPassword": "current_password",
    "newPassword": "new_password_min_8_chars"
  }
  ```
  
  **Response:**
  ```json
  {
    "success": true,
    "message": "Password updated successfully. Please log in again on all devices."
  }
  ```
  
  **Security Notes:**
  - New password must be at least 8 characters
  - Current password must be correct
  - All refresh tokens are revoked (forces re-login on all devices)
}
